title: The Lone Ranger S01E01-02
description:
The Lone Ranger

The Sole Survivor of a posse of Texas Rangers ambushed by a gang of desperados, John Reid was left for dead and nursed back to health by Tonto (Jay Silverheels), a friendly Indian whom he had once helped. With a black mask and silver bullets from the mine he discovered with his brother, one of the slain Rangers, Reid sets out astride his horse, Silver, to right the wrongs of the West as The Lone Ranger (Clayton Moore)

Episode 01 Enter the Lone Ranger

In the beginning of his three-part origin, "Enter the Lone Range", half-breed scout Vince Collins (George Lewis) leads Captain Reid (Tristram Coffin) and his men into the trap for Butch Cavendish (Glenn Strange). Then,

Episode 02 The Lone Ranger Fights On

As Kemo Sabe (trusty scout) saves a silver-white horse from death and enlists ex-Ranger Jim Blane (Ralph Littefield), whom Cavendish frames for murder, to look after the mine.

Approximately 48 Minutes 
Converted from VHS
